{"id":89428,"title":"Preoperative management of anticoagulation and antiplatelet agents.","abstract":"This article describes current literature and treatment plans for managing anticoagulation and antiplatelet agents in patients presenting with hip fractures. Indications for anticoagulation and antiplatelet agents are discussed, and management techniques for when patients present with hip fractures are reviewed.","date":"2014-04-11","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24721362","annotations":[{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.194967,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Anticoagulant","weight":0.0574785,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anticoagulant"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.0227187,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Hip fracture","weight":0.0188318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip_fracture"},{"name":"Espionage","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Espionage"},{"name":"Hip","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hip"},{"name":"Indication (medicine)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Bone fracture","weight":0.0157947,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone_fracture"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0136738,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Antiplatelet drug","weight":0.0120594,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antiplatelet_drug"}]}
